import React from 'react';
import { StyleSheet, View, Text, TouchableOpacity, CheckBox } from 'react-native';
import { TextInput } from 'react-native-gesture-handler';
import { Ionicons } from '@expo/vector-icons'; 

import styles from './styles';

function LogSignIn(props) {
  const { navigation } = props

  const toggleSwitch = () => (previousState=>!previousState)

  return (
    <View style={styles.container}>
      <Text style={styles.text}>LogSignIn</Text>
      <View style={styles.signUpBox}>
        <Text>Sign up here</Text>
        <Text>email</Text>
        <TextInput placeholder="input email"/>
        <Text>password</Text>
        <TextInput placeholder="input password"/>
        <Text>check password</Text>
        <TextInput placeholder="check password"/>
        <Text>role</Text>
        <View style={styles.checkBoxContainer}>
          <CheckBox style={styles.checkBox}/><Text style={styles.label}>user</Text>
        </View>
        <View style={styles.checkBoxContainer}>
          <CheckBox style={styles.checkBox}/><Text style={styles.label}>authenticated user</Text>
        </View>
        <View style={styles.checkBoxContainer}>
          <CheckBox style={styles.checkBox}/><Text style={styles.label}>doctor(?)</Text>
        </View>
        <TouchableOpacity
          style={styles.buttonContainer}>
          <Text style={styles.buttonText}>SignUp</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
      </View>
      <TouchableOpacity
        style={styles.buttonContainer}
        onPress={() => navigation.navigate('Home')}>
        <Text style={styles.buttonText}>Home</Text>
      </TouchableOpacity>
    </View>
  )
}

export default LogSignIn
